1.0.name: wordpress/p2p-wpml
1.0.description:
p2p-wpml is a WordPress plugin that integrates iCanLocalize's WPML and Posts 2 Posts.

The following table shows version compatibility between this plugin, other plugins and WordPress:

  • P2P-WPML 1.0

    • P2P 0.8
    • WPML 2.3.3, 2.3.4
    • WordPress 3.2.1

  • P2P-WPML 1.1

    • P2P 1.3.1
    • WPML 2.5.2
    • WordPress 3.4.1

  • P2P-WPML 1.2.1

    • P2P 1.4.1
    • WPML 2.5.2
    • WordPress 3.4.1

  • P2P-WPML 1.2.2

    • P2P 1.5.2
    • WPML 2.7.1
    • WordPress 3.5.1

  • P2P-WPML 1.2.3

    • P2P 1.5.2
    • WPML 2.7.1
    • WordPress 3.5.1, 3.5.2

This plugin has been only tested with the above version combinations; different versions of WordPress
